welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Redland, where Southern hospitality meets vibrant city life! Get ready to indulge in our famous BBQ, explore our charming downtown, and soak up the warm sun. Enjoy your stay and discover all that Redland has to offer."

terminals.name: Terminal A
terminals.description: The oldest terminal at DCA, serving primarily domestic flights.

terminals.name: Terminal B/C
terminals.description: The largest and newest terminal at DCA, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal D
terminals.description: A smaller terminal at DCA, serving primarily regional flights.

wifi.note: Limited to 45 minutes per device per day.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Frederick Municipal Airport serves both commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Frederick Municipal Airport caters to private and corporate flights.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.
